#: .\martialarts.json
msgid "Survivor Sledge-Fu"
msgstr "倖存者大錘功夫"

#. ~ Description for martial art '{'str': 'Survivor Sledge-Fu'}'
#: .\martialarts.json
msgid ""
"You have started to become rather proficient in handling heavy weaponry. "
"Sledge-Fu allows you to bully an opponent using your strength until the "
"right moment presents itself to swing your weapon properly for a killing "
"blow."
msgstr "你已經開始相當熟練地使用重型武器。大錘功夫讓你能夠利用力量壓制對手，直到合適的時機出現，再揮動武器給予致命一擊。"

#. ~ Initiate message for martial art '{'str': 'Survivor Sledge-Fu'}'
#: .\martialarts.json
msgid "You roll your neck and get ready to shatter your enemies."
msgstr "你轉動脖子，準備粉碎你的敵人。"

#. ~ Initiate message for martial art '{'str': 'Survivor Sledge-Fu'}'
#: .\martialarts.json
#, c-format
msgid "%s rolls their neck menacingly."
msgstr "%s 威脅性地轉動脖子。"

#: .\martialarts.json
msgid "Intimidating Figure"
msgstr "威懾形象"

#. ~ Description of buff 'Intimidating Figure' for martial art '{'str':
#. 'Survivor Sledge-Fu'}'
#: .\martialarts.json
msgid ""
"No man, machine or monstrosity can get through you and your strength. \n"
"\n"
"+2 Block attempts, -3.0 Dodge skill, blocked damage reduced by 70%% of Strength."
msgstr ""
"沒有人、機器或怪物能夠突破你和你的力量。\n"
"\n"
"+2 格擋嘗試，-3.0 閃避技能，格擋傷害減少 70%% 的力量值。"

#: .\martialarts.json
msgid "Moving Bulk"
msgstr "移動巨軀"

#. ~ Description of buff 'Moving Bulk' for martial art '{'str': 'Survivor
#. Sledge-Fu'}'
#: .\martialarts.json
msgid ""
"Moving your weight around makes it hard to take hits strategically, but it does prove useful for extra swing speed. \n"
"\n"
"-2 Block attempts, blocked damage increased by 70%% of Strength.\n"
"+10%% bonus to bashing damage.\n"
"Lasts 1 turn."
msgstr ""
"移動你的體重使得難以策略性地承受攻擊，但這確實對額外的揮擊速度很有用。\n"
"\n"
"-2 格擋嘗試，格擋傷害增加 70%% 的力量值。\n"
"+10%% 的打擊傷害加成。\n"
"持續 1 回合。"

#: .\martialarts.json
msgid "Eager For Contact"
msgstr "渴望接觸"

#. ~ Description of buff 'Eager For Contact' for martial art '{'str':
#. 'Survivor Sledge-Fu'}'
#: .\martialarts.json
msgid ""
"You dodged. Next time, you'll take the hit and make them pay properly. \n"
"\n"
"-3.0 Dodge skill\n"
"Lasts 3 turns.  Stacks 3 times."
msgstr ""
"你閃避了。下次，你會承受攻擊並讓他們付出應有的代價。\n"
"\n"
"-3.0 閃避技能\n"
"持續 3 回合。可疊加 3 次。"

#: .\martialarts.json
msgid "Survivor Flail-Fu"
msgstr "倖存者鏈枷功夫"

#. ~ Description for martial art '{'str': 'Survivor Flail-Fu'}'
#: .\martialarts.json
msgid ""
"You have started to become very proficient in handling heavy weaponry. "
"Flail-Fu lets you redirect opponents as the chain wishes, or whirl the head "
"for a heavy blow."
msgstr "你已經開始非常熟練地使用重型武器。鏈枷功夫讓你能夠根據鏈條的意願引導對手，或者旋轉頭部進行重擊。"

#. ~ Initiate message for martial art '{'str': 'Survivor Flail-Fu'}'
#: .\martialarts.json
msgid "You grip your flail confidently and start swaying the chain."
msgstr "你自信地握住鏈枷，開始擺動鏈條。"

#. ~ Initiate message for martial art '{'str': 'Survivor Flail-Fu'}'
#: .\martialarts.json
#, c-format
msgid "%s grips their flail and sways the chain idly."
msgstr "%s 握住鏈枷，隨意地擺動著鏈條。"

#: .\martialarts.json
msgid "Metal Must Flow"
msgstr "金屬必須流動"

#. ~ Description of buff 'Metal Must Flow' for martial art '{'str': 'Survivor
#. Flail-Fu'}'
#: .\martialarts.json
msgid ""
"Your flail must keep spinning at all costs. \n"
"\n"
"+1.0 Dodge skill"
msgstr ""
"你的鏈枷必須不惜一切代價保持旋轉。\n"
"\n"
"+1.0 閃避技能"

#: .\martialarts.json
msgid "Swift Mass"
msgstr "迅捷質量"

#. ~ Description of buff 'Swift Mass' for martial art '{'str': 'Survivor
#. Flail-Fu'}'
#: .\martialarts.json
msgid ""
"Dodging an attack only quickens your weapon!\n"
"\n"
"+10%% bashing damage.\n"
"Enables \"Stunning Blow\" technique.\n"
"Lasts 1 turns.  Stacks 3 times."
msgstr ""
"閃避攻擊只會讓你的武器更快！\n"
"\n"
"+10%% 打擊傷害。\n"
"啟用“眩暈打擊”技巧。\n"
"持續 1 回合。可疊加 3 次。"

#: .\martialarts.json
msgid "Survivor Glove-Fu"
msgstr "倖存者手套功夫"

#. ~ Description for martial art '{'str': 'Survivor Glove-Fu'}'
#: .\martialarts.json
msgid ""
"You're not unused to the concept of killing things with your own hands. "
"Glove-Fu lets you show the Zs the real definition of a smackdown with "
"unrelenting, heavy hitting powercombos."
msgstr "你並不陌生於用自己的雙手殺死東西的概念。手套功夫讓你能夠向殭屍展示什麼是真正的重擊，通過持續不斷的強力連擊。"

#. ~ Initiate message for martial art '{'str': 'Survivor Glove-Fu'}'
#: .\martialarts.json
msgid "You assume a sturdy stance and keep one arm cocked and loaded."
msgstr "你採取穩固的站姿，並將一隻手臂蓄勢待發。"

#. ~ Initiate message for martial art '{'str': 'Survivor Glove-Fu'}'
#: .\martialarts.json
#, c-format
msgid "%s assumes a sturdy stance and keeps an arm ready."
msgstr "%s 採取穩固的站姿，並保持一隻手臂準備就緒。"

#: .\martialarts.json
msgid "Ready"
msgstr "準備就緒"

#. ~ Description of buff 'Ready' for martial art '{'str': 'Survivor Glove-
#. Fu'}'
#: .\martialarts.json
msgid ""
"You're ready. Your fighting implements are ready. They always will be. \n"
"\n"
"+2 Block attempts, -1.0 Dodge skill, blocked damage reduced by 50%% of Strength."
msgstr ""
"你已準備就緒。你的戰鬥工具也已就緒。它們永遠都會如此。\n"
"\n"
"+2次格擋嘗試，-1.0點閃避技能，格擋傷害減少力量值的50%。"

#: .\martialarts.json
msgid "Eager For Smackdown"
msgstr "渴望痛擊"

#. ~ Description of buff 'Eager For Smackdown' for martial art '{'str':
#. 'Survivor Glove-Fu'}'
#: .\martialarts.json
msgid ""
"You dodged. Next time, you'll take the hit so you can begin the smackdown. \n"
"\n"
"-3.0 Dodge skill\n"
"Lasts 3 turns.  Stacks 3 times."
msgstr ""
"你閃避了。下一次，你將承受攻擊以便開始痛擊。\n"
"\n"
"-3.0點閃避技能\n"
"持續3回合。可疊加3次。"

