msgstr "車削"

#: .\items\armor.json
msgid "pair of extra-light survivor gloves"
msgid_plural "pairs of extra-light survivor gloves"
msgstr[0] "一雙超輕型倖存者手套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of extra-light survivor gloves', 'str_pl':
#. 'pairs of extra-light survivor gloves'}
#: .\items\armor.json
msgid ""
"A pair of very light Kevlar-lined cloth gloves, modified to be as easy to "
"wear as normal gloves while providing considerable protection under rough "
"conditions."
msgstr "一雙非常輕便的凱夫拉襯裡布手套，經過改良，穿戴起來如同普通手套一樣輕鬆，同時在惡劣環境下提供可觀的保護。"

#: .\items\armor.json
msgid "pair of extra-light survivor boots"
msgid_plural "pairs of extra-light survivor boots"
msgstr[0] "一雙超輕型倖存者靴子"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of extra-light survivor boots', 'str_pl':
#. 'pairs of extra-light survivor boots'}
#: .\items\armor.json
msgid ""
"A pair of very light Kevlar-lined cloth boots, modified to provide "
"considerable protection from harm, even when ankle-deep in the dead."
msgstr "一雙非常輕便的凱夫拉襯裡布靴，經過改良，即使深陷屍群也能提供可觀的傷害防護。"

#: .\items\armor.json
msgid "light survivor helmet"
msgid_plural "light survivor helmets"
msgstr[0] "輕型倖存者頭盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'light survivor helmet'}
#: .\items\armor.json
msgid ""
"A customized, Kevlar-armored helmet, modified with leather reinforcements to"
" provide maximum comfort and considerable protection from harm given the "
"weight."
msgstr "一款定製的凱夫拉裝甲頭盔，採用皮革加固改良，在保證重量的前提下提供最大舒適度和可觀的傷害防護。"

#: .\items\armor.json
msgid "extra-light survivor mask"
msgid_plural "extra-light survivor masks"
msgstr[0] "超輕型倖存者面罩"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'extra-light survivor mask'}
#: .\items\armor.json
msgid ""
"A custom-built, Kevlar-lined gas mask that covers the face and eyes.  "
"Provides excellent protection from smoke and teargas, and considerable "
"protection from shrapnel.  It must be prepared before use."
msgstr "一款定製、凱夫拉襯裡的防毒面具，覆蓋面部和眼睛。對煙霧和催淚瓦斯提供極佳防護，對彈片也有可觀保護。使用前必須準備。"

#: .\items\armor.json
msgid "extra-light survivor hood"
msgid_plural "extra-light survivor hoods"
msgstr[0] "超輕型倖存者兜帽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'extra-light survivor hood'}
#: .\items\armor.json
msgid ""
"A customized Kevlar-lined cloth hood, very light and considerably durable."
msgstr "一款定製的凱夫拉襯裡布兜帽，非常輕便且相當耐用。"

#: .\items\armor.json
msgid "extra-light survivor suit"
msgid_plural "extra-light survivor suits"
msgstr[0] "超輕型倖存者套裝"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'extra-light survivor suit'}
#: .\items\armor.json
msgid ""
"A very lightweight Kevlar-lined jumpsuit, nearly as easy to move in as if it"
" were just cotton. Protects from the elements as well as from some harm."
msgstr "一件非常輕便的凱夫拉襯裡連體服，活動起來幾乎像純棉一樣自如。既能抵禦惡劣天氣，也能提供一定的傷害防護。"

#: .\items\armor.json
msgid "pair of superheavy survivor gloves"
msgid_plural "pairs of superheavy survivor gloves"
msgstr[0] "一雙超重型倖存者手套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of superheavy survivor gloves', 'str_pl':
#. 'pairs of superheavy survivor gloves'}
#: .\items\armor.json
msgid ""
"A pair of extreme, heavily customized, steel-plated armored Kevlar gloves, "
"modified to provide maximum protection under extreme conditions. Mobility "
"comes second."
msgstr "一雙極致、高度定製的鋼板裝甲凱夫拉手套，經過改良，在極端條件下提供最大防護。機動性次之。"

#: .\items\armor.json
msgid "pair of superheavy survivor boots"
msgid_plural "pairs of superheavy survivor boots"
msgstr[0] "一雙超重型倖存者靴子"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of superheavy survivor boots', 'str_pl':
#. 'pairs of superheavy survivor boots'}
#: .\items\armor.json
msgid ""
"A pair of extreme, customized kevlar boots, heavily armored with steel and "
"modified to provide maximum protection from serious harm, even when knee-"
"deep in hell itself."
msgstr "一雙極致、定製的凱夫拉靴，採用重型鋼板裝甲改良，即使深陷地獄也能提供最大程度的嚴重傷害防護。"

#: .\items\armor.json
msgid "superheavy survivor helmet"
msgid_plural "superheavy survivor helmets"
msgstr[0] "超重型倖存者頭盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'superheavy survivor helmet'}
#: .\items\armor.json
msgid ""
"A ridiculously customized, heavily armored steel and kevlar helmet, modified"
" to provide protection from even the most extreme harm."
msgstr "一款極其定製、重型裝甲的鋼和凱夫拉頭盔，經過改良，能防護最極端的傷害。"

#: .\items\armor.json
msgid "superheavy survivor mask"
msgid_plural "superheavy survivor masks"
msgstr[0] "超重型倖存者面罩"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'superheavy survivor mask'}
#: .\items\armor.json
msgid ""
"A custom-built, tri-filter steel gas mask that covers the face and eyes.  "
"Provides beyond excellent protection from smoke, teargas, and shrapnel.  It "
"must be prepared before use."
msgstr "一款定製、三濾芯鋼製防毒面具，覆蓋面部和眼睛。對煙霧、催淚瓦斯和彈片提供超乎尋常的防護。使用前必須準備。"

#: .\items\armor.json
msgid "heavy survivor hood"
msgid_plural "heavy survivor hoods"
msgstr[0] "重型倖存者兜帽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'heavy survivor hood'}
#: .\items\armor.json
msgid ""
"A heavily customized, heavily armored steel, leather and kevlar hood, "
"designed to provide maximum protection from harm."
msgstr "一款高度定製、重型裝甲的鋼、皮革和凱夫拉兜帽，旨在提供最大傷害防護。"

#: .\items\armor.json
msgid "superheavy survivor suit"
msgid_plural "superheavy survivor suits"
msgstr[0] "超重型倖存者套裝"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'superheavy survivor suit'}
#: .\items\armor.json
msgid ""
"An extreme, hand-built combination armor made from a steel-reinforced "
"bulletproof vest and thick metal plates attached to leather to cover the "
"limbs.  Protects from the elements as well as from serious harm, for those "
"who want to push the limits of unpowered armor."
msgstr ""
"一套極致、手工打造的組合裝甲，由鋼加固防彈背心和厚金屬板附著在皮革上覆蓋四肢製成。既能抵禦惡劣天氣，也能防護嚴重傷害，適合那些想挑戰無動力裝甲極限的人。"

#: .\items\armor.json
msgid "heavy survivor leather robe"
msgid_plural "heavy survivor leather robes"
msgstr[0] "重型倖存者皮革長袍"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'heavy survivor leather robe'}
#: .\items\armor.json
msgid ""
"A full-size, full-thickness, solidly and lovingly sewn leather robe meant to"
" be worn over other clothes. It has no pockets, to maximize protection. "
"While very, very heavy and encumbering, it protects well from serious harm."
msgstr ""
"一件全尺寸、全厚度、結實且精心縫製的皮革長袍，設計用於穿在其他衣物外。沒有口袋，以最大化防護。雖然非常沉重且妨礙行動，但對嚴重傷害防護良好。"

#: .\items\armor.json
msgid "survivor rubber undersuit"
msgid_plural "survivor rubber undersuit"
msgstr[0] "倖存者橡膠內襯服"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'survivor rubber undersuit'}
#: .\items\armor.json
msgid ""
"A handmade, skintight acid-resistant rubber-plastic combo suit. It is "
"cleverly designed so as to not limit movement as much as one would think, "
"but this leaves cotton gaps at the joints which are susceptible to "
"penetration. Either way, it will protect well from things such as acid."
msgstr ""
"一件手工製作、緊身耐酸的橡膠塑料組合服。設計巧妙，對行動的限制比想象中小，但關節處留有棉質縫隙易受穿透。無論如何，它能很好地防護酸液等物質。"

#: .\items\armor.json
msgid "pair of survivor dark plate gauntlets"
msgid_plural "pairs of survivor dark plate gauntlets"
msgstr[0] "一雙倖存者暗色板甲護手"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of survivor dark plate gauntlets',
#. 'str_pl': 'pairs of survivor dark plate gauntlets'}
#: .\items\armor.json
msgid ""
"A ridiculously customized, extreme-looking and insanely heavy pair of dark-"
"tinted plate gauntlets. The knuckles flange up and the fingers end in "
"spikes, which makes this pair of gloves understandably hard to use. However,"
" they protect really, really well, and look super fancy to boot."
msgstr ""
"一雙極其定製、外觀極端且異常沉重的暗色調板甲護手。指關節凸起，手指末端帶刺，使得這雙手套使用起來相當困難。然而，它們防護效果極佳，而且看起來超級炫酷。"

#: .\items\armor.json
msgid "pair of survivor dark plate sabatons"
msgid_plural "pairs of survivor dark plate sabatons"
msgstr[0] "一雙倖存者暗色板甲戰靴"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of survivor dark plate sabatons', 'str_pl':
#. 'pairs of survivor dark plate sabatons'}
#: .\items\armor.json
msgid ""
"A ridiculously customized, extreme-looking and insanely heavy pair of dark-"
"tinted plate sabatons. These terrifying boots practically threaten to "
"crumble the earth with every step, and although their weight and stylish, "
"angular construction make them a little impractical, they will protect your "
"foot even if you decide to kick a tank-bot during a duel to the death. And "
"they'll look good doing it."
msgstr ""
"一雙經過荒謬定製、外觀極端且沉重得離譜的暗色調板甲戰靴。這雙駭人的靴子幾乎每一步都威脅著要踏碎大地，儘管其重量和稜角分明的時尚構造讓它們略顯不實用，但即使你在生死決鬥中決定去踢一個坦克機器人，它們也能保護你的腳。而且它們看起來還很酷。"

#: .\items\armor.json
msgid "survivor dark quad-horned greathelm"
msgid_plural "survivor dark horned greathelmets"
msgstr[0] "倖存者暗色四角巨盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor dark quad-horned greathelm', 'str_pl':
#. 'survivor dark horned greathelmets'}
#: .\items\armor.json
msgid ""
"This is the king of helmets. The spiky horns signal to all that the wearer "
"is the bringer of metal-plated death. Its sturdy, beyond-solid steel "
"construction keeps anything that dares go against it at bay."
msgstr "這是頭盔之王。尖刺狀的角向所有人宣告佩戴者是帶來金屬覆面死亡的存在。其堅固無比、超越實心的鋼結構能將任何膽敢對抗之物拒之門外。"

#: .\items\armor.json
msgid "survivor dark plate armor"
msgid_plural "survivor dark plate armors"
msgstr[0] "倖存者暗色板甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor dark plate armor'}
#: .\items\armor.json
msgid ""
"A ridiculously customized, extreme-looking and insanely heavy set of dark-"
"tinted plate armor. It's rife with impractical-looking flanges and "
"questionable design choices, especially in the shoulder area, but in a world"
" where opponents don't know how to exploit those, all they do is add to the "
"protection. And... one cannot deny, it looks darn stylish."
msgstr ""
"一套經過荒謬定製、外觀極端且沉重得離譜的暗色調板甲。它佈滿了看似不實用的凸緣和值得商榷的設計選擇，尤其是在肩部區域，但在這個對手不知道如何利用這些弱點的世界裡，它們只會增加防護。而且……不可否認，它看起來非常時髦。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "Closer Looks At Guns In History"
msgid_plural "copies of Guns In History"
msgstr[0] "歷史槍械細覽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Closer Looks At Guns In History', 'str_pl':
#. 'copies of Guns In History'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"A textbook that goes through many influential guns of history and "
"intricately details their inner workings, from flintlock to modern day. It "
"also names and explains more than a few experimental guns with a heavy "
"emphasis on minute, unique mechanical details, which should let the "
"enterprising survivor like you really figure out how guns work."
msgstr ""
"一本教科書，梳理了歷史上許多有影響力的槍械，並詳細闡述了它們從燧發槍到現代的內部工作原理。它還命名並解釋了不少實驗性槍械，重點強調微小、獨特的機械細節，這應該能讓像你這樣有進取心的倖存者真正弄清楚槍械是如何工作的。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "workshop log"
msgid_plural "workshop logs"
msgstr[0] "工坊日誌"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'workshop log', 'str_pl': 'workshop logs'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"A log of the workshop's business, work, commissions, things like that. It's "
"useless at first glance, but there's very many technical details that the "
"experienced craftsman could learn from. The handwritten last chapter also "
"has very interesting ideas on how the workshop's machinery could be "
"improved."
msgstr ""
"一份記錄工坊業務、工作、委託等事項的日誌。乍一看毫無用處，但其中包含了許多有經驗的工匠可以借鑑的技術細節。手寫的最後一章還提出了關於如何改進工坊機械的非常有趣的想法。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'workshop log', 'str_pl': 'workshop logs'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"A log of the workshop's business, work, commissions, things like that. It's "
"useless at first glance, but somewhere among the endless metal trinkets is a"
" wildly detailed blueprint for a... magnetic rail rifle? The order reads "
"FULFILLED."
msgstr "一份記錄工坊業務、工作、委託等事項的日誌。乍一看毫無用處，但在無數金屬小飾品中，藏有一份極其詳細的……磁軌步槍藍圖？訂單上寫著“已完成”。"

#: .\items\gun.json
msgid "Survivor machined belt-fed shotgun"
msgid_plural "Survivor machined belt-fed shotguns"
msgstr[0] "倖存者機加工彈鏈供彈霰彈槍"

#: .\items\gun.json
msgid ""
"This is a professional-looking homemade machine-shotgun made to take custom,"
" high-quality shotshell belts. It has semi, burst and full-auto fire modes "
"and many rails for modification beyond its already-solid foundation. This "
"was definitely made with love and care, and even makes a decent bashing "
"implement if push comes to shove."
msgstr ""
"這是一把外觀專業的自制機加工霰彈槍，設計用於使用定製的高質量霰彈彈鏈。它擁有半自動、點射和全自動射擊模式，並在其已經堅固的基礎上提供了許多用於改裝的導軌。這絕對是傾注了愛心和細心製作的，甚至在必要時也能當作不錯的敲擊工具。"

#: .\items\gun.json
msgid "semi-auto"
msgstr "半自動"

#: .\items\gun.json
msgid "2 rd."
msgstr "2發。"

#: .\items\gun.json
msgid "auto"
msgstr "自動"

#: .\items\gun.json
msgid "Survivor machined shotgun revolver"
msgid_plural "Survivor machined shotgun revolvers"
msgstr[0] "倖存者機加工霰彈左輪手槍"

#: .\items\gun.json
msgid ""
"This is a massive, professional-looking revolver chambered in full-size "
"shotshells. It's made nearly entirely of steel to be as weighty as possible "
"to absorb recoil, and comes with many attachment points for modifications. "
"This was definitely made with love and care, and even makes a decent bashing"
" implement if push comes to shove."
msgstr ""
"這是一把巨大的、外觀專業的左輪手槍，使用全尺寸霰彈。它幾乎完全由鋼材製成，以儘可能增加重量來吸收後坐力，並帶有許多用於改裝的附件安裝點。這絕對是傾注了愛心和細心製作的，甚至在必要時也能當作不錯的敲擊工具。"

#: .\items\gun.json
msgid "Survivor rail rifle"
msgid_plural "Survivor rail rifles"
msgstr[0] "倖存者磁軌步槍"

#: .\items\gun.json
msgid ""
"This overpowered and overengineered, professional-looking and MASSIVE rifle "
"was designed to deliver electromagnetically-driven obliteration right "
"through whatever obstacle that lies in front of it, be it building, vehicle "
"or a horde of walking dead.  However, the hefty bulk and weight of this "
"weapon compared to most contemporary rifles makes it somewhat cumbersome to "
"wield; not to mention that it consumes UPS charges at a tremendous rate, "
"making it impractical for use in prolonged engagements. Either way, this was"
" definitely made with love and care."
msgstr ""
"這把威力過強、過度設計、外觀專業且體型巨大的步槍，旨在通過電磁驅動將毀滅直接送達前方任何障礙物，無論是建築、車輛還是一群行屍走肉。然而，與大多數現代步槍相比，該武器的龐大體積和重量使其揮舞起來有些笨拙；更不用說它以驚人的速度消耗UPS電量，使其在持久戰中不切實際。無論如何，這絕對是傾注了愛心和細心製作的。"

#: .\items\gunmod.json
msgid "underbarrel axehead"
msgid_plural "underbarrel axeheads"
msgstr[0] "下掛斧頭"

#: .\items\gunmod.json
msgid ""
"This is a stout axehead, like one on the end of a medieval battleaxe. It has"
" a railed handle on the back, so you could attach it to a gun to make it a "
"very dangerous, if unwieldy, melee weapon."
msgstr ""
"這是一個結實的斧頭，類似於中世紀戰斧末端的樣式。它的背面有一個帶導軌的握柄，因此你可以將其安裝在槍上，使其成為一種非常危險（儘管可能笨重）的近戰武器。"

#: .\items\items.json
msgid "lathing rig"
msgid_plural "lathing rigs"
msgstr[0] "車床設備"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'lathing rig'}
#: .\items\items.json
msgid ""
"This is a very large lathing rig, including tools aside from the big "
"rotating bit. It runs on batteries and will allow you to lathe anything from"
" fancy table legs to precision gun receivers, albeit inefficiently."
msgstr ""
"這是一套非常大的車床設備，除了大型旋轉部件外還包括其他工具。它依靠電池運行，可以讓你車削從精美的桌腿到精密的槍機匣等各種東西，儘管效率不高。"

#: .\items\items.json
msgid "machining rig"
msgid_plural "machining rigs"
msgstr[0] "機加工設備"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'machining rig'}
#: .\items\items.json
msgid ""
"This is a neatly arranged, self-contained workbench kit of various precision"
" machining and metalworking tools, from handheld to integrated. Some things "
"can be used without power, but the heavy duty built-in tools will require "
"batteries."
msgstr ""
"這是一套整齊排列、自成一體的工作臺套件，包含各種精密機加工和金屬加工工具，從手持式到集成式都有。有些工具無需電力即可使用，但重型內置工具需要電池供電。"

#: .\items\items.json
msgid "shotshell ammo belt linkage"
msgid_plural "shotshell ammo belt linkages"
msgstr[0] "霰彈彈鏈連接件"

#: .\items\magazines.json
msgid "metal shotshell ammo belt"
msgid_plural "metal shotshell ammo belts"
msgstr[0] "金屬霰彈彈鏈"

#: .\items\melee.json
msgid "survivor sledge"
msgid_plural "survivor sledges"
msgstr[0] "倖存者大錘"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor sledge'}
#: .\items\melee.json
msgid ""
"A highly customized sledgehammer with carefully-placed rubber along the "
"handle and a wicked-looking steel head, sharp on one end and square on "
"another. Designed for post-apocalyptic swinging pleasure, though you could "
"also use it as a clumsy tool."
msgstr ""
"一把高度定製的大錘，手柄上精心放置了橡膠，鋼製錘頭看起來兇悍，一端尖銳，另一端方正。專為後末日時代的揮擊樂趣而設計，不過你也可以把它當作笨拙的工具使用。"

#: .\items\melee.json
msgid "survivor claymore"
msgid_plural "survivor claymores"
msgstr[0] "倖存者巨劍"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor claymore'}
#: .\items\melee.json
msgid ""
"This is a ridiculously large and heavy custom-made sword. If you can get it "
"moving, you can destroy anything."
msgstr "這是一把大得離譜、沉重無比的定製劍。如果你能揮動它，就能摧毀一切。"

#: .\items\melee.json
msgid "survivor flail"
msgid_plural "survivor flails"
msgstr[0] "倖存者連枷"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor flail'}
#: .\items\melee.json
msgid ""
"A highly customized, two-handed flail with carefully-placed rubber along the"
" handle and a wicked-looking steel head, slightly spiked, mostly blunt, and "
"very heavy. The chain is long enough to make using this a complicated "
"endeavor, but if used properly by a skilled survivor, it could probably "
"crush a skull or five."
msgstr ""
"一把高度定製的雙手連枷，手柄上精心包裹著橡膠，配有一個外觀兇險的鋼製頭部，略帶尖刺，大部分為鈍面，且非常沉重。鏈條足夠長，使得使用它成為一項複雜的挑戰，但如果由熟練的倖存者正確使用，它或許能砸碎一個甚至五個頭骨。"

#: .\items\melee.json
msgid "survivor fighting gauntlet"
msgid_plural "survivor fighting gauntlets"
msgstr[0] "倖存者戰鬥護手"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor fighting gauntlet', 'str_pl': 'survivor
#. fighting gauntlets'}
#: .\items\melee.json
msgid ""
"A customized metal gauntlet resembling a flanged mace, strapped securely to "
"one's hand. Strange to get used to, but it will wildly improve punching "
"power."
msgstr "一個定製的金屬護手，形似凸緣釘頭錘，牢固地綁在手上。起初使用會感到彆扭，但它能極大地提升拳擊威力。"

#: .\monsters\monsters.json
msgid "monstrous zombie technician"
msgid_plural "monstrous zombie technicians"
msgstr[0] "怪物般的殭屍技師"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'monstrous zombie technician'}
#: .\monsters\monsters.json
msgid ""
"A terrifying goliath, forced to hunch over by the weight of improvised "
"conveyor belt armor on its back. It could rival a semi-truck and win."
msgstr "一個可怕的巨人，因背上臨時拼湊的傳送帶裝甲的重量而被迫駝背。它足以與半掛卡車匹敵並取勝。"

#: .\monsters\speech.json
msgid "an EARTHSHAKING roar!!!"
msgstr "一聲驚天動地的咆哮！！！"

#: .\overmap\overmap_terrain_artisan.json
msgid "artisan metalworks"
msgstr "工匠金屬工坊"

#: .\overmap\overmap_terrain_artisan.json
msgid "artisan metalworks roof"
msgstr "工匠金屬工坊屋頂"
